# Walkthrough — Endee RAG Document Q&A System

## What Was Built

A complete **Retrieval Augmented Generation (RAG)** system using **Endee** as the vector database. Users upload PDF/TXT documents, the system indexes them in Endee, and answers natural language questions using semantic retrieval + Llama 3 via Groq.

