## GitHub Push Instructions

```bash
cd /Users/chandankumar/Desktop/Assignment

git init
git add .
git commit -m "Initial commit: Endee RAG Document Q&A System"
git remote add origin https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/endee-rag-qa.git
git branch -M main
git push -u origin main
```

> **Important**: Before pushing, make sure you have:
> - ⭐ Starred https://github.com/endee-io/endee
> - 🍴 Forked https://github.com/endee-io/endee to your account
> - Created your project repo (`endee-rag-qa` or similar)
